Privacy Policy for Alfa Boss

We at Alfa Boss respect your privacy and are committed to protecting it. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect the personal information we receive from you when you use our mobile application, Alfa Boss.

What Information We Collect

We do not collect any personal data or information through our app. We do not use cookies, analytics tools or any other tracking software to collect data about our users.

How We Use Your Information

Since we don’t collect any personal data or information about you, your privacy is not affected by our application. Therefore, we don’t share or sell your data to third parties.

How We Protect Your Information

As Alfa Boss does not collect any personal data or information, there is no need to worry about your information getting lost, misused, or disclosed to unauthorized parties.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may periodically update this privacy policy, If there are any changes, we will post a notice on our website and update the effective date at the top of this page.

Contact Information

If you have any questions or comments about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at support@alfaboss.com.

Last updated: September 2021.
